WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.300 --> 00:00:02.033
Get me a tissue, please.

2
00:00:08.400 --> 00:00:09.133
Hey

3
00:00:09.133 --> 00:00:11.900
How did you come up with the idea of sending flowers to Mr. Xuanyuan?

4
00:00:13.666 --> 00:00:15.500
Governor Xuanyuan loves Wang Qi

5
00:00:15.600 --> 00:00:16.800
Unmarried for many years

6
00:00:16.800 --> 00:00:19.100
It can be seen that he has deep affection for Wang Qi

7
00:00:19.100 --> 00:00:20.566
I didn't expect it.

8
00:00:21.000 --> 00:00:22.500
Your observation skills are not bad

9
00:00:22.666 --> 00:00:25.666
Yeah, I've been a reporter for four years.

10
00:00:25.666 --> 00:00:26.166
But

11
00:00:26.166 --> 00:00:28.966
It took a long time to find this

12
00:00:28.966 --> 00:00:31.133
You have to make it up to me, it's really capable

13
00:00:31.133 --> 00:00:32.400
So much effort

14
00:00:32.900 --> 00:00:34.300
What do you want to get together?

15
00:00:34.400 --> 00:00:36.466
That's definitely a raise.

16
00:00:36.566 --> 00:00:39.600
Miss Xie, let me toast you.

17
00:00:43.300 --> 00:00:46.700
Wait, this soup looks like mine.

18
00:00:47.166 --> 00:00:49.466
Forget it, I haven't had one anyway

19
00:00:56.700 --> 00:00:57.466
Miss Xia

20
00:00:57.466 --> 00:00:59.766
The governor heard that you found this painting

21
00:00:59.766 --> 00:01:01.100
If you have the chance

22
00:01:01.200 --> 00:01:02.566
He wants to thank you in person

23
00:01:03.333 --> 00:01:04.500
Thank you Governor for your love

24
00:01:04.500 --> 00:01:05.500
Happy cooperation

25
00:01:07.966 --> 00:01:10.466
Ah, it's finally over.

26
00:01:10.966 --> 00:01:11.766
Xi Shao

27
00:01:12.100 --> 00:01:15.066
We should also talk about what we just said

28
00:01:15.400 --> 00:01:17.333
You just asked me what I wanted

29
00:01:17.333 --> 00:01:18.500
I've thought about it.

30
00:01:18.800 --> 00:01:21.000
Can you find it for me?

31
00:01:21.533 --> 00:01:23.600
What's wrong with you, daughter-in-law?

32
00:01:25.733 --> 00:01:26.533
Ah!

